OL,3,CPossible jail term for 24-year-old
OL,4,Cover inciting racial hatred on Twitter
OL,6,FA 24-year-old man faces jail after
OL,7,Fadmitting inciting racial hatred on
OL,8,Fsocial media.
OL,10,FNathan Thompson, of Whickham View,
OL,11,FNewcastle, made offensive comments on
OL,12,FTwitter, the site now known as X,
OL,13,Fabout black people, Jews, Muslims and
OL,14,Fthose from the LGBT+ community.
OL,16,FThe court heard that he also mentioned
OL,17,Fwhite supremacy in the tweets made
OL,18,Fbetween April and July last year.
