OL,3,CPossible jail term for 24-year-old
OL,4,Cover inciting racial hatred on Twitter
OL,6,FThompson admitted nine counts of
OL,7,Finciting racial hatred online and two
OL,8,Fmalicious communications offences in
OL,9,Fan appearance at Newcastle
OL,10,FMagistrates' Court on Monday 4 March.
OL,12,FHe was told he would be sentenced at
OL,13,FNewcastle Crown Court on 3 April as
OL,14,Fthe offences were too serious for the
OL,15,Fmagistrates' court to deal with.
OL,17,FClaire Armstrong, prosecuting, said a
OL,18,Fpossible jail sentence for the
OL,19,Foffences had a starting point of three
OL,20,Fyears.
