OL,3,CPossible jail term for 24-year-old
OL,4,Cover inciting racial hatred on Twitter
OL,6,FThe court was told that Thompson had
OL,7,Fbecome socially isolated and spent a
OL,8,Flot of time on his computer when the
OL,9,Foffences were committed.
OL,11,FGregg Stephens, defending, said: "He
OL,12,Fis a young lad who is quite isolated
OL,13,Fand socially vulnerable.
OL,15,F"He has mental health issues, doesn't
OL,16,Fmix with people and spends a lot of
OL,17,Ftime on his computer.
OL,19,F"He has got himself connected to this
OL,20,Fright-wing stuff which you can find
OL,21,Fonline."
