OL,4,Cover inciting racial hatred on Twitter
OL,6,FMr Stephens said what was posted went
OL,7,Fwell beyond expressing free speech and
OL,8,FThompson now realised it was "wholly
OL,9,Finappropriate".
OL,11,FHe said Thompson had never been in
OL,12,Ftrouble before and sought support for
OL,13,Fhis mental health problems after he
OL,14,Fwas arrested.
OL,16,FMr Stephens said: "He doesn't
OL,17,Fnecessarily believe in the things he
OL,18,Fhas been putting online, he has been
OL,19,Fmisguided, rather than someone who is
OL,20,Fa genuine danger."
